theorem finite_stable_under_composition : stable_under_composition @finite :=
  by
  introv R hf hg
  exact hg.comp hf
#align finite_stable_under_composition finite_stable_under_composition
finite_stable_under_base_change:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `tensor_product -/
theorem finite_stable_under_base_change : stable_under_base_change @finite :=
  by
  refine' stable_under_base_change.mk _ finite_respects_iso _
  classical
    introv h
    skip
    replace h : module.finite R T := by
      convert h
      ext
      rw [algebra.smul_def]
      rfl
    suffices module.finite S (tensor_product S R T)
      by
      change module.finite _ _
      convert this
      ext
      rw [algebra.smul_def]
      rfl
    exact infer_instance
#align finite_stable_under_base_change finite_stable_under_base_change
finite_respects_iso:
theorem finite_respects_iso : respects_iso @finite :=
  by
  apply finite_stable_under_composition.respects_iso
  intros
  exact finite.of_surjective _ e.to_equiv.surjective
#align finite_respects_iso finite_respects_iso
